  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of the study is to predict outcomes of patients on extracorporeal membrane
      oxygenation (ECMO) therapy by correlating cytokines and inflammatory cell patterns to
      clinical outcomes using data collected in the ECMO Registry at Spectrum Health.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
